{"tid":1695454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑有手足顯靈，求幫手睇吓","createTime":"2019-11-05T15:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T16:13:10.000Z","uid":235301,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ffdb756acbc9974f6d02fcb22cfd09958fe6a5","tid":1695454,"uid":235301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:53:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GoeaQKR__CM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGoeaQKR__CM&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=767240f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GoeaQKR__CM</a><br />\n<br />\n首先，條片紀錄咗唔同曱甴對記者嘅粗暴無理行為<br />\n<br />\n但睇到 09:03 果陣時..<br />\n<br />\n有個完全無gear，著黑衫嘅男仔，雙目無神咁企左係d曱甴記者之間<br />\n<br />\n係鏡頭閃過之後就搵激都搵唔到個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjqAW2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjqAW2.png&h=2439137a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信到今時今刻，一定唔會有記者連gear都唔上就上場，但就係有一個男仔無gear咁企左係中間<br />\n<br />\n但片見到，個男仔企係度好似無人見到佢咁<br />\n<br />\n如果有位後生仔，無gear咁企係度，仲唔俾班曱甴拉？<br />\n<br />\n我睇完真即刻諗係831<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我無辦法fact check到，所以想大家一齊睇下<br />\n<br />\n係未真係有手足顯靈，跟住班曱甴<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n解散警隊，刻不容緩</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0683a2a94f2ebaba76288c4eec3f5165f2761d70","tid":1695454,"uid":235301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"ba75abe83474b099fb641b259abbcbf502850fa7","tid":1695454,"uid":235301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:54:13.000Z